  <compounddef id="DNS" kind="page">
    <compoundname>DNS</compoundname>
    <title>DNS$ Function</title>
    <briefdescription>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para><programlisting filename=".basic"><codeline><highlight class="normal">DNS$(string-expression)</highlight></codeline>
</programlisting></para>
<para>Resolves a <bold>hostname</bold> into an <bold>IP address string</bold>. If the hostname cannot be resolved, an error is raised.</para>
<para><hruler/>
</para>
<sect3 id="DNS_1autotoc_md556">
<title>Examples</title>
<para><programlisting filename=".basic"><codeline><highlight class="normal">PRINT<sp/>DNS$(&quot;retrorocket.dev&quot;)</highlight></codeline>
</programlisting></para>
<para>Might produce:</para>
<para><programlisting><codeline><highlight class="normal">141.95.6.222</highlight></codeline>
</programlisting></para>
<para><programlisting filename=".basic"><codeline><highlight class="normal">REM<sp/>Use<sp/>DNS$<sp/>before<sp/>connecting<sp/>a<sp/>socket</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">host$<sp/>=<sp/>&quot;irc.libera.chat&quot;</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">ip$<sp/>=<sp/>DNS$(host$)</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">PRINT<sp/>&quot;Connecting<sp/>to<sp/>&quot;;<sp/>host$;<sp/>&quot;<sp/>(&quot;;<sp/>ip$;<sp/>&quot;)&quot;</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">CONNECT<sp/>fd,<sp/>ip$,<sp/>6667</highlight></codeline>
</programlisting></para>
<para><hruler/>
</para>
</sect3>
<sect3 id="DNS_1autotoc_md558">
<title>Notes</title>
<para><itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>Always returns an IPv4 address in dotted decimal format (<computeroutput>a.b.c.d</computeroutput>).</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Name resolution is performed via the operating system’s network stack.</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Failures (e.g. host not found, no network) return the value &quot;0.0.0.0&quot;</para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
<para><hruler/>
</para>
<para><bold>See also:</bold> <ref refid="CONNECT" kindref="compound">CONNECT</ref> · <ref refid="SOCKSTATUS" kindref="compound">SOCKSTATUS</ref> </para>
</sect3>
